	"description": "In this post, I will lay down the major principles of Functional Programming,\nstarting with the basics and then exploring more advanced concepts.\n\nI&#x27;ll first talk about why you should bother with Functional Programming, that is\nwhen it&#x27;s useful and when it&#x27;s not.\n\nWe will cover a lot of stuff here, so please go at your own pace. Take some\nbreaks and naps between your reading sessions and do the exercises I propose.\n\nOf course, you can skip sections or go back and fourth depending on your needs.\n",
